description: [``botocore``] Adding new attribute to disable IMDS v1 APIs for fleet, Image Builder and AppBlockBuilder instances.
[``botocore``] Migrated to Smithy. No functional changes
[``botocore``] Update endpoint-rules client to latest version

[``botocore``] Added support for S3OutputPathExtension and Filename parameters to the InvokeEndpointAsync API to allow users to customize the S3 output path and file name for async inference response payloads.

[``botocore``] This release introduces AWS Signer Data Plane SDK client supporting GetRevocationStatus API. The new client enables AWS PrivateLink connectivity with both private DNS and VPC endpoint URLs.
[``botocore``] Add support for AssociationDispatchAssumeRole in AWS SSM State Manager.
[``botocore``] Adding a new enum attribute(statusReason) to TrustedAdvisorAPI response. This attribute explains reasoning behind check status for certain specific scenarios.
